\begin{aligned} \frac{1}{b_{n+1}}+1=\frac{3\left(\frac{1}{b_{n}}+1\right)-4}{9\left(\frac{1}{b_{n}}+1\right)+15}=\frac{3 b_{n}+1}{9 b_{n}+24}=\frac{1}{3}\left(\frac{1}{b_{n}}+1\right), \end{aligned}
即 $b_{n+1}=3 b_{n}$, 又 $b_{1}=\frac{1}{a_{1}-1}=\frac{1}{2}$, 所以 $\left\{b_{n}\right\}$ 是首项为 $\frac{1}{2}$, 公比为 3 的等比数列, 于是 $b_{n}=\frac{1}{2} \cdot 3^{n-1}$, 即
\begin{aligned} a_{n}=\frac{1}{b_{n}}+1=\frac{2}{3^{n-1}}+1. \end{aligned}
